Koemei module for Kaltura Mediaspace
============

Version 0.1.0

Installation
--------

Copy the content of this archive into the mediaspace/modulesCustom folder

Usage
--------

1. Register on https://www.koemei.com
2. Enable the module
3. All your existing and future media will be automatically transcribed

